:0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:22:36.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n不過牛唔飲水唔撳得牛頭低<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n聽日下晝三點愛丁堡要人！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1783274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1783274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2CTsQkj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2CTsQkj.jpg&h=8e37d259&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f6f77ff54d550d041400201a28094ed6e9a59c2","tid":1783231,"uid":267915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b059f09c30fcd386d9591407762474b72d51fb4d","tid":1783231,"uid":96,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:40:34.000Z","msg":"食藥有咩咁垃圾先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假設男女拍拖又信得過對方出面唔會搞三搞四嘅話 食藥中招個機會仲少過用安全套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你用安全套又可能會唔小心穿左 跟住有左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係冇諗住要bb而又意外懷孕嘅情況之下 男人損失大啲定女人損失大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好講到食藥單單係為左俾男人屌咁啦 首先呢啲你情我願 第二就係食藥都係女仔保障自己嘅一種方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:23:03.000Z","msg":"意外懷孕梗係女人損失大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個B生係個女人度，又要孕吐，又要陀住個肚十個月重到腰痛，出門口又唔方便，生仔個下宮縮大半日個B先肯出黎，個B唔夠位出黎又要剪開陰道口，完全係搵命搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />生完身體又虛身材又走樣，仲要24小時候命餵奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假設男人係唔想負責任既，衰衰地咪一走了之唔諗數，好少少既俾幾千蚊條女去家計會落仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假設個男仔真係負責任既好仔，又會損失係邊度？最多咪照顧個女人所需錢同時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />健康同生產風險同埋餵B食奶個責任都唔係由男人承擔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食藥扑野當然冇問題，我好贊成食藥+戴套雙管齊下避孕因為我真係好撚驚意外懷孕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但如果條仔係為左扑野爽逼條女食藥係絕對仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為食藥既風險都係由條女承擔（雖然細風險）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以食藥必須係雙方有共識/條女自願先ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}